subject: Biathlon
lead_paragraph: The two-time Olympic biathlon champion Emil Hegle Svendsen edged Tarjei Boe by a tenth of a second at a World Cup 12.5-kilometer pursuit in Hochfilzen, Austria, for a Norwegian 1-2 finish.
